00:11:22,000 --> 00:11:24,399
Orangku ingin mematuhi peraturan...

121
00:11:24,399 --> 00:11:26,600
Jangan ikut campur.

122
00:11:26,600 --> 00:11:28,559
Kalau aku menolak?

123
00:11:30,600 --> 00:11:34,500
Aku memiliki kedudukan dan reputasi.

124
00:11:34,500 --> 00:11:36,200
