Bagi kami, ini masih pagi...

170
00:14:52,799 --> 00:14:54,799
Maka, tidurlah dalam damai.

171
00:15:03,700 --> 00:15:05,437
Kecuali kau.

172
00:15:07,100 --> 00:15:09,099
Mari kita minum.

173
00:15:34,100 --> 00:15:36,100
