179
00:15:54,200 --> 00:15:57,000
Ayo. Atau mulut kita akan dicabik-cabik.

180
00:15:57,000 --> 00:15:58,600
Oke?

181
00:15:58,600 --> 00:16:02,200
Jangan menatapku begitu.
Ingat posisimu.

182
00:16:04,399 --> 00:16:06,000
Sampai jumpa.

183
00:16:09,234 --> 00:16:11,299
